===Etymology===
;hedgehog

:Its graph is also used to {{zh-l|彙|category, class}}, which is perhaps a variant of {{zh-l|類}} without the latter's ''l-'' initial. Also note {{zh-l|彙|hedgehog}}'s Cantonese pronunciation ''leoi<sup>6</sup>''.({{zh-ref|Bodman, 1980}}; {{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}})

:{{der|zh|sit}}; cognate with {{cog|lus|kuh||porcupine's quill, porcupine}} and {{cog|lus|sakuh|sa'''kuh'''|porcupine}}. In Tibeto-Burman cognates *''k-'' is seemingly a prefix.({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}})

;category, class

:If {{och-l|彙|tr=*wəs}} were related to {{och-l|類|tr=*rus}}, it may be a form whose initial *''r-'' had been treated as a prefix and dropped.

